<h1>Resend Activation Email</h1>
<p>
  Didn't receive the activation email?  Please be patient, the activation email can take up to 15 minutes to reach your inbox.  In addition, please check
  spam folders for the email.  Please also be sure 'accounts@energyfolks.com' is allowed to send email to your account.
</p>
<p>
  To resend the activation email, please enter the email address you registered with in the box below.  If you still have
  trouble activation your account, email us at <a href="mailto:contact@energyfolks.com">contact@energyfolks.com</a>.
</p>
<div class='center'>
    <%= form_tag('/users/resend_activation') do %>
        <%= raw(iframe_form) %>
        Email Address: <input type="text" name="email">
        <input type="hidden" name="step" value='2'>
        <BR>
        <button type="submit">Resend Activation Email</button>
    <% end %>
</div>